Somehow a creationist went to heaven and talks with God. - Lord, tell me how you created the Universe? - Well, the Big Bang, particles and antiparticles, exponential expansion, well, you yourself know. - And how did you create all living things - Well, abiogenesis, then evolution, and slowly everything happened, well, your scientists figured everything out a long time ago. - And how did you create a man, a man? - Well, primates, evolution again, well, not without difficulty, of course. .. so you even study it at school. Didn't you go to school? - But the Bible says about seven days and the like! - And how could I explain to the savages there about antiparticles, abiogenesis and evolution?!